{"tid":2088726,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[厲害了我的國］中國反制！要求美聯社等四美媒 一周內報告中國業務","createTime":"2020-07-01T09:41:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T09:59:38.000Z","uid":239336,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f68737327b5f07e154489dbfa4a5a2921052f7f9","tid":2088726,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T09:41:15.000Z","msg":"路透社報道指，中國外交部要求美聯社（AP）、美國合眾國際社（UPI）、美國哥倫比亞廣播公司（CBS）、美國全國公共廣播電台（NPR）在一周內，書面交代其公司在中國的業務。<br />\n<br />\n中方報道補充，上述四美媒需要在一周內書面申報中國境內所有工作人員、財務、經營、所擁有不動產訊息。<br />\n中國外交部發言人趙立堅指出，中方措施反制美方打壓中國媒體駐美機構，是正當防衞，並稱美方暴露標榜的「新聞自由」的虛偽。趙立堅稱，美國方面有關做法是基於冷戰思維和意識形態偏見，嚴重損害中國媒體的聲譽及形象，嚴重影響中國媒體在美國的正常運作，嚴重干擾中美正常人文交流，「暴露其自我標榜的所謂『新聞自由』的虛偽性。」中國敦促美國立即改弦更張、糾正錯誤，停止對中國媒體的政治打壓和無理限制。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200701/LJNCEQALPRA5ZNJDGBWVR6MPSA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200701%2FLJNCEQALPRA5ZNJDGBWVR6MPSA%2F&d=oa%2BbSijZO%2BDWYSsAyiffbqWONrq76Y1XZ%2F%2BBeLOBzgc%3D&h=53c2e324\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200701%2FLJNCEQALPRA5ZNJDGBWVR6MPSA%2F&h=2d48b4ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200701/LJNCEQALPRA5ZNJDGBWVR6MPSA/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b1d6d95906b754ac4a98a12d7c8055b91c934e4","tid":2088726,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T09:50:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62d49363e6ff302597827af372885aa9ac906b14","tid":2088726,"uid":197640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f68737327b5f07e154489dbfa4a5a2921052f7